# Recorded with vhs (github.com/charmbracelet/vhs):
#   vhs demos/maude/demo.tape
Output demos/maude/demo.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 960
Set Height 640
Set Padding 12
Set TypingSpeed 60ms

Hide
Type "go run ./demos/maude"
Enter
Sleep 3s
Show

Sleep 1s
Type "Can you refactor the render pipeline?"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2.5s

Type "Show me a diff of the changes"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Sleep 2s
